CONTRIBUTING.md
     1‚Üí# Contributing
     3‚Üí1. [Fork it](https://help.github.com/articles/fork-a-repo/)
     4‚Üí2. Install dependencies (`npm install`)
     5‚Üí3. Create your feature branch (`git checkout -b my-new-feature`)
     6‚Üí4. Commit your changes (`git commit -am 'Added some feature'`)
     7‚Üí5. Test your changes (`npm test`)
     8‚Üí6. Push to the branch (`git push origin my-new-feature`)
     9‚Üí7. [Create new Pull Request](https://help.github.com/articles/creating-a-pull-request/)
    10‚Üí
    11‚Üí## Testing
    13‚ÜíWe use [TAP](https://github.com/tapjs/node-tap) to write tests. Run our test suite with this command:
    14‚Üí
    15‚Üí```
    16‚Üínpm test
    17‚Üí```
    18‚Üí
    19‚Üí## Code Style
    21‚ÜíWe use [standard](https://www.npmjs.com/package/standard) and [editorconfig](http://editorconfig.org) to maintain code style and best practices. Please make sure your PR adheres to the guides by running:
    22‚Üí
    23‚Üí```
    24‚Üínpm run lint
    25‚Üí```
